General.Name: Elektroimportoren As
General.Description: Elektroimportøren AS, together with its subsidiaries, sells electrical installation products to private and professional customers in Norway. It offers electro materials; lighting products; cables; and other electro installation products, as well as heating and ventilation products. The company sells products through department stores and e-commerce. The company was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Oslo, Norway.
